Genomenet model maxlen 150

Source: R/data.R
model_self_genomenet_maxlen_150.Rd

Serialized keras model for "bacteria", "virus-no-phage","virus-phage" classification. Can be loaded to workspace via data(self_genomenet_model_maxlen_150). Use keras::unserialize_model to transform to keras model or load with load_model_self_genomenet(maxlen = 150) function call.
